_sText:
Basic fun map, smash the square cubes to send others to their deaths or use standard weapons to kill them. The intention is for terrorists to plant the bomb at the bombsite floating underneath the arena by rushing it from their base and counter-terrorists defend. Game follows the basic principles of glasstrap, but with neon lighting (beware of strobe effect) and a bombsite.

BOTs not supported, they get stuck at the spawn area.
